75","tid":1727592,"uid":86961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f456797a53d2d8af7c4b300fa5ead9022f35068","tid":1727592,"uid":44437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"咁大家就一齊出力問候環保署，叫佢哋交數啦！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋有兩個Facebook，大嘥鬼同黃錦星，Inbox問清楚佢，大家都放心啲。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大嘥鬼 Big Waster<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bigwaster.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbigwaster.hk&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=91b3bf74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bigwaster.hk</a><br />\n黃錦星 Wong Kam Sing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wongkamsing.hksarg/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwongkamsing.hksarg%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=4f6ccf17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wongkamsing.hksarg/</a>"},{"pid":"a58e2fd3e24ab6506d97601f3d80d6b660ce1307","tid":1727592,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"琴日聽商台報天氣報告連空氣污染指數都唔提"},{"pid":"db7ec97ec48e546a614be28ce6e90a9acd4cf49e","tid":1727592,"uid":44437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"致：enquiry@epd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n致環境局常任秘書長/環境保護署署長鄭美施女士, JP<br />\n<br />\n「要求盡快公佈二噁英監測數據」<br />\n<br />\n近日網上流傳警方使用中國製造催淚彈會釋出大量二噁英污染環境，本人瀏覽 貴署網頁(<a href=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/data/dioxin_1.html?fbclid=IwAR0Lnki0thVktCrQww2oHIYinoUZNoobuO5tcd7PQazuVemNnP_FxlsaaIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Fdata%2Fdioxin_1.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Lnki0thVktCrQww2oHIYinoUZNoobuO5tcd7PQazuVemNnP_FxlsaaIU&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=c16215c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/data/dioxin_1.html?fbclid=IwAR0Lnki0thVktCrQww2oHIYinoUZNoobuO5tcd7PQazuVemNnP_FxlsaaIU</a><br />\n)時亦發現「周邊二噁英監測摘要」，由今年九月開始便沒有公佈數字。現望 貴署能盡快公佈監測數據，以釋疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n環境保護署的抱負乃為香港締造一個健康宜人的環境，祈望 貴署能盡快回覆，以挽回香港人對環境質素的信心。<br />\n<br />\n祝工作順利！<br />\n<br />\nXXX上<br />\n2019年11月16日"},{"pid":"959c36df8d27a66c4854ccd0d3af1ce896f50997","tid":1727592,"uid":44437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50W2BNs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50W2BNs.png&h=960aa315&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b9ac11005fc303d80abddf7427b1bb736ae10ff","tid":1727592,"uid":42712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a58e2fd3e24ab6506d97601f3d80d6b660ce1307","tid":1727592,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"琴日聽商台報天氣報告連空氣污染指數都唔提"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"就算提，outlier數據可能會被剔走"},{"pid":"be012757afb14d8b06a657816bfb4e9c3e93ebcd","tid":1727592,"uid":96310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e0d31583b43aa8914cda70d932474b955ae1188","tid":1727592,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b9ac11005fc303d80abddf7427b1bb736ae10ff","tid":1727592,"uid":42712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a58e2fd3e24ab6506d97601f3d80d6b660ce1307","tid":1727592,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"琴日聽商台報天氣報告連空氣污染指數都唔提"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"就算提，outlier數據可能會被剔走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:15:31.000